Method-WeakCallback
===================

Build callbacks that incoke some method in an object using weak
references.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries: 

  Test::More

